The paper discusses the use of deep learning networks to solve the Travelling Salesman Problem, which is a classic problem in computer science and optimization. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves designing a customised deep learning network, which falls under the Deep Learning (cs.DS) sub-category.
